{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"681f9398c1","title":"关于对阁锡山的态度致叶剑英、刘鼎电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"835ecc8fad","index":0,"year":1936,"month":10,"day":23,"articleId":"681f9398c1"}],"tags":[{"id":"bcecfeaa3a","name":"叶剑英","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b89f97d558","type":"paragraph","text":"关于对阁锡山的态度致叶剑英、刘鼎电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"681f9398c1"},{"id":"a6cf642f4d","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年10月23日）剑、刘：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"681f9398c1"},{"id":"d461eded5f","type":"paragraph","text":"经过季毅或另设他法向陶锡山表示下列客点","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"681f9398c1"},{"id":"be0e331b69","type":"paragraph","text":"一、完全同情普绥当局及其军队对日抗战捍卫疆土的决心与行动，他们的这种决心与行动将获得全国人民的拥护，苏维埃与红军将竭力以全力以为之助。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"681f9398c1"},{"id":"e0287d6a19","type":"paragraph","text":"二、我们十分盼望与普绥当局成立谅解以至订立抗日协定","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"681f9398c1"},{"id":"3afa3b435c","type":"paragraph","text":"三、只要普绥当局真正抗日，而不与日本妥协，红军在未得晋绥当局同意之前，决不冒然向普绥开进","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"681f9398c1"},{"id":"d5b684faba","type":"paragraph","text":"四、在双方谅解之后，红军依约进入划定之地区与防线，担任一定战斗任务，并服从统一之指挥，红军不干涉普绥当局之行政事宜。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"681f9398c1"},{"id":"6949a95648","type":"paragraph","text":"五、某方援助我们可担任介绍","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"681f9398c1"},{"id":"5b7479609b","type":"paragraph","text":"东十月二十三日十六时","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"681f9398c1"}],"page":{"id":"3a7b10cd80","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"681f9398c1","start":251,"end":251}}}},"__N_SSG":true}